WEBVTT

01:37.860 --> 01:41.039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.140 --> 01:43.920
[Episode 14]

01:46.280 --> 01:47.340
How did they reply?

01:48.710 --> 01:50.640
They told me
they are still considering it.

01:50.640 --> 01:51.710
Nothing is certain.

01:51.710 --> 01:54.070
We also sent people over to check.

01:54.310 --> 01:56.509
They either said the boss was not there,

01:56.640 --> 01:58.350
or they were vague.

01:58.759 --> 01:59.620
I was thinking,

01:59.789 --> 02:02.250
since the agreement
between us has expired,

02:02.310 --> 02:05.000
I'll let the front office,
the rooms division,

02:05.000 --> 02:06.640
and the finance department
settle the accounts

02:06.640 --> 02:08.699
and take back the rooms this weekend.

02:18.120 --> 02:19.630
Mr. Ji, please take the time to sign

02:19.630 --> 02:22.240
these two documents.

02:22.520 --> 02:24.630
Then I'll take my leave.

02:24.990 --> 02:25.520
Okay.

02:43.060 --> 02:45.350
[Senior]

02:47.740 --> 02:48.060
[Xue Rui]

02:52.680 --> 02:53.630
These folders

02:53.630 --> 02:56.680
contain all the hotel's revenue bills.

02:57.280 --> 02:58.000
For how to compile

02:58.000 --> 02:58.680
and categorize them,

02:58.680 --> 03:00.280
just follow last year's template.

03:00.280 --> 03:01.520
Review my ass!

03:02.470 --> 03:03.310
Listen carefully:

03:03.310 --> 03:05.770
get the general manager's signature first!

03:07.560 --> 03:09.480
Isn't the general manager's
signature here?

03:08.670 --> 03:09.540
[Fund Review Form] [GM Signature: Ji Feng]

03:09.630 --> 03:12.040
Here we need Mr. Wei's signature!

03:16.320 --> 03:17.410
Don't you understand?

03:17.410 --> 03:19.810
You don't even know
who you are working for.

03:22.280 --> 03:23.140
Director Xue.

03:25.100 --> 03:25.900
Director Xue,

03:27.400 --> 03:29.950
is the occupancy rate
calculated incorrectly?

03:29.950 --> 03:31.520
[Housekeeping Department
Occupancy Rate Report]

03:30.040 --> 03:31.630
It's 10 percentage points
lower than last week.

03:31.520 --> 03:32.400
[Total Rooms] [Occupied Rooms]

03:32.010 --> 03:34.420
It was 58% last Friday.

03:32.420 --> 03:38.870
[Occupancy Rate Line Chart]

03:34.680 --> 03:35.740
After the weekend,

03:35.750 --> 03:36.190
it

03:37.000 --> 03:38.750
suddenly dropped to 48%.

03:39.240 --> 03:39.900
Take a look.

04:07.160 --> 04:10.250
[Resignation Report]

04:10.610 --> 04:13.270
[Application: Xue Rui]

04:15.340 --> 04:19.230
[Ji Feng]

04:42.770 --> 04:44.680
♪ Life is full of ♪

04:45.730 --> 04:48.380
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

04:49.909 --> 04:53.760
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

04:55.190 --> 04:55.600
[Delivery List]

04:55.350 --> 04:57.350
♪ All those confusions ♪

04:55.659 --> 04:57.320
[HSKP Department] [Project] [Balance]

04:57.320 --> 04:58.110
[May 31, Sales Department Banquet]

04:57.940 --> 05:01.660
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

04:58.130 --> 04:58.820
[Sales Commission: 12,000 Not Recorded]

05:02.540 --> 05:06.540
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

05:09.940 --> 05:12.060
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

05:13.470 --> 05:15.390
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

05:17.220 --> 05:21.060
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

05:22.740 --> 05:24.540
♪ Busy and restless ♪

05:25.140 --> 05:28.570
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

05:29.910 --> 05:33.970
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

05:35.980 --> 05:38.440
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

05:39.659 --> 05:41.630
♪ Don't look back ♪

05:42.659 --> 05:44.390
♪ I've already learned ♪

05:45.210 --> 05:48.920
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

05:49.740 --> 05:51.310
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

05:52.200 --> 05:56.270
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

05:57.120 --> 06:00.060
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

06:00.760 --> 06:03.250
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

06:03.980 --> 06:05.620
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

06:10.760 --> 06:13.220
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

06:11.900 --> 06:12.830
Tail number 2867.

06:12.830 --> 06:14.440
To the high-speed rail station.

06:14.440 --> 06:16.310
♪ Don't look back ♪

06:17.550 --> 06:19.210
♪ I've already learned ♪

06:19.950 --> 06:23.750
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

06:20.830 --> 06:21.960
You don't need to go.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.140
I came back myself.

06:24.510 --> 06:25.780
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

06:24.630 --> 06:25.720
Sir, I'm not taking the ride.

06:25.720 --> 06:27.040
-It's okay.
-You can still open the order;

06:26.760 --> 06:30.950
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

06:27.040 --> 06:27.560
I'll pay online.

06:27.560 --> 06:28.240
Okay.

06:30.520 --> 06:31.890
By going back on my word,

06:31.900 --> 06:34.430
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

06:32.020 --> 06:33.680
I've completely offended everyone

06:33.680 --> 06:34.680
at Yiting Siji.

06:35.420 --> 06:36.290
You have to take care of me.

06:35.530 --> 06:37.790
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

06:36.640 --> 06:37.350
I will.

06:37.390 --> 06:39.110
I'll take care of your future.

06:38.700 --> 06:40.110
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

06:39.240 --> 06:39.900
Don't brag.

06:40.040 --> 06:40.600
Also,

06:40.680 --> 06:41.960
I canceled my lease.

06:42.240 --> 06:43.240
I'm homeless now.

06:43.360 --> 06:44.650
I'll arrange the rest.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.659
First, go to HR and get onboarded.

06:46.720 --> 06:47.480
Why in such a hurry?

06:47.480 --> 06:49.340
I'm afraid you'll run away again.

06:49.800 --> 06:50.360
Let's go.

06:55.800 --> 06:56.240
Okay.

06:57.480 --> 06:58.240
I got it.

07:10.600 --> 07:11.240
Mr. Wei,

07:11.950 --> 07:15.070
add a desk to Mr. Ji's office.

07:17.190 --> 07:20.070
[Qian][Wei]

07:20.620 --> 07:21.440
Sorry to put you through this.

07:21.440 --> 07:22.770
Be my assistant for now.

07:23.020 --> 07:24.840
Once I figure out the management team,

07:24.840 --> 07:26.170
I'll send you back to
the finance department.

07:26.170 --> 07:27.100
That's nothing.

07:27.480 --> 07:27.830
Come,

07:28.240 --> 07:29.640
come over and take a look.

07:30.120 --> 07:32.180
I'll walk you through the situation.

07:32.800 --> 07:34.350
Wei Siyuan's "iron triangle."

07:34.350 --> 07:35.930
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

07:34.480 --> 07:36.480
Qian Xun from the sales department,

07:36.520 --> 07:37.560
Huang Chengmin
from the finance department,

07:37.330 --> 07:42.300
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

07:37.720 --> 07:40.050
and Feng Kaixin from the HSKP Department,

07:40.070 --> 07:42.070
are all relatives.

07:44.560 --> 07:45.240
Is it firm?

07:45.800 --> 07:46.430
Yes.

07:46.430 --> 07:47.000
Xiang,

07:47.250 --> 07:48.370
come, say hi to mom.

07:49.070 --> 07:51.800
One is the cousin
of Wei Siyuan's father-in-law,

07:51.820 --> 07:53.030
Be careful.

07:53.800 --> 07:55.600
another is his brother-in-law,

07:57.040 --> 07:59.440
and this one is his wife's
younger brother.

08:00.390 --> 08:02.270
They have total control over
Purong Hotel's finances.

08:02.270 --> 08:03.120
Xiang.

08:03.120 --> 08:03.920
Touch any one of them,

08:03.920 --> 08:06.140
and you're up against all four.

08:06.920 --> 08:07.920
Take it easy!

08:12.680 --> 08:13.510
Baby.

08:14.540 --> 08:16.500
[Yunji Equestrian Club]

08:14.560 --> 08:15.250
Thank you.

08:15.720 --> 08:15.920
Come on.

08:15.920 --> 08:16.600
Go, go, go.

08:16.870 --> 08:18.560
Come on, kids, get your milk.

08:18.580 --> 08:19.160
Come, come, come.

08:19.160 --> 08:19.930
Cheers.

08:20.040 --> 08:21.800
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

08:20.540 --> 08:23.330
[Yunji Equestrian Club]

08:21.800 --> 08:22.830
Bottoms up.

08:25.040 --> 08:26.560
Of the two major clients
Purong Hotel lost,

08:26.560 --> 08:27.560
one is Shijing Tech,

08:27.560 --> 08:29.360
and the other is Zhanpeng Industry.

08:29.360 --> 08:32.620
They have very good personal relationships
with Qian Xun.

08:35.440 --> 08:36.120
Qian,

08:36.360 --> 08:37.700
your business is our business.

08:37.700 --> 08:38.700
Good, good, good.

08:39.360 --> 08:40.289
Mr. Zheng, come.

08:40.520 --> 08:42.780
If you want to
renew the contract next year,

08:42.780 --> 08:44.670
Mr. Qian, it just takes one word from you.

08:44.670 --> 08:45.810
Good, good.

08:47.000 --> 08:49.090
Thanks for your help.

08:49.150 --> 08:49.790
Come on!

08:50.030 --> 08:52.000
Here's to our successful cooperation.

08:52.000 --> 08:53.390
Putting it all together,

08:53.390 --> 08:54.170
if you audit the accounts,

08:54.170 --> 08:55.360
they'll delete clients.

08:55.360 --> 08:56.120
That's basically telling you

08:56.120 --> 08:58.180
the cost of messing with Feng Kaixin.

08:58.240 --> 08:58.910
Yes.

08:59.480 --> 09:01.460
I told you not to take on this mess.

09:01.600 --> 09:02.360
Just let Kuanli

09:02.360 --> 09:04.550
buy out this whole nest of vipers.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.120
Let's not dwell on the past.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.600
Since you chose to fight back,

09:07.600 --> 09:09.780
we need to know our enemy.

09:11.200 --> 09:12.750
I know Feng Kaixin.

09:13.390 --> 09:16.070
He's just a good-for-nothing.

09:16.510 --> 09:17.840
He only survives
because Wei Siyuan protects him.

09:17.840 --> 09:19.790
[Huang] [Qian] [Wei] [Feng]

09:17.940 --> 09:20.200
But Huang Chengmin is much more cunning.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.980
You can tell from his accounts

09:22.270 --> 09:23.080
that he

09:23.080 --> 09:24.340
keeps a low profile,

09:24.840 --> 09:26.080
and he's the sneaky type.

09:26.080 --> 09:27.810
The head of the "iron triangle"

09:27.840 --> 09:28.720
is Qian Xun.

09:29.790 --> 09:31.270
In Purong Hotel, Wei Siyuan

09:31.270 --> 09:32.730
makes the most illicit money.

09:32.730 --> 09:35.270
Besides Wei Siyuan, he's probably
the one taking kickbacks.

09:35.270 --> 09:36.530
So by doing this,

09:37.270 --> 09:39.080
you're messing with his interests.

09:39.080 --> 09:41.270
Watch out, he might
sabotage your performance.

09:41.270 --> 09:43.630
After all, he's in charge of
the sales department.

09:43.630 --> 09:45.200
The economic lifeline of the whole hotel

09:45.200 --> 09:46.600
is in his hands.

09:47.960 --> 09:49.160
I thought of that too.

09:49.390 --> 09:52.080
So I don't plan to rely on him
for the first deal.

09:53.610 --> 09:55.210
Then what are you going to do?

09:55.870 --> 09:56.270
Here.

10:02.690 --> 10:03.900
[Inbox]

10:02.710 --> 10:03.770
Libo Group.

10:03.920 --> 10:04.760
[Libo Group APAC Chief Brand Officer]

10:04.020 --> 10:05.730
For the first deal,
I have to handle it personally.

10:04.780 --> 10:05.630
[Marcos Yang Visits Purong Hotel]

10:05.850 --> 10:07.840
That way, we can make sure
nothing goes wrong—

10:07.840 --> 10:09.320
and it also sends them a message.

10:09.320 --> 10:11.180
You focus on bringing in revenue,

10:11.330 --> 10:12.350
I'll help cut costs.

10:12.350 --> 10:13.270
You start auditing.

10:13.270 --> 10:14.870
We'll hit from both sides.

10:27.120 --> 10:29.360
I've caused you three a lot of trouble.

10:29.680 --> 10:30.950
I am here

10:31.270 --> 10:32.670
to sincerely apologize.

10:33.080 --> 10:34.200
Let me toast you.

10:34.220 --> 10:35.070
Bottoms up!

10:47.620 --> 10:48.720
Alright.

10:49.150 --> 10:51.750
Your business is our business.

10:52.050 --> 10:53.780
Don't treat us like strangers.

10:59.510 --> 11:00.390
You guys,

11:00.410 --> 11:02.170
don't just stick together.

11:02.630 --> 11:05.000
The new general manager is young

11:05.000 --> 11:06.510
and unfamiliar with the place.

11:06.510 --> 11:09.630
You should take the initiative
to look after him.

11:14.710 --> 11:15.830
Look after him?

11:16.480 --> 11:17.080
Sure.

11:17.510 --> 11:19.110
I'll "take good care" of him.

11:19.440 --> 11:20.240
I promise

11:20.240 --> 11:22.640
I'll kick him out
in less than three months.

11:27.030 --> 11:30.180
I know that guy Ji's background.

11:30.270 --> 11:33.240
Didn't he just study abroad
for a few years?

11:30.490 --> 11:33.870
[General Manager's Office]

11:39.510 --> 11:40.430
[Inventory Ledger]

11:47.040 --> 11:47.760
[Notice on Receiving Libo Group]

11:47.790 --> 11:48.600
[APAC CBO Marcos Yang]

11:51.030 --> 11:52.480
[Notice on Receiving Libo Group]

11:52.500 --> 11:54.100
[APAC CBO Marcos Yang]

12:00.690 --> 12:01.520
[Send]
[Customer information of Purong Hotel]

12:03.300 --> 12:03.440
[Sending emails]

12:03.500 --> 12:04.550
[Sending successfully]

12:12.760 --> 12:15.730
[Purong Directors Group Chat]

12:13.870 --> 12:14.870
Directors,

12:15.270 --> 12:16.910
please check the client information
in the email.

12:16.910 --> 12:18.410
Prepare to receive Libo Group's

12:18.410 --> 12:19.770
APAC CBO

12:19.800 --> 12:21.320
Marcos Yang.

12:27.120 --> 12:28.600
[Okay.]

12:31.040 --> 12:37.020
[Okay.]

12:40.030 --> 12:40.640
Kaixin,

12:41.550 --> 12:42.410
reply quickly.

12:42.950 --> 12:43.500
No.

12:43.910 --> 12:44.910
I won't reply.

12:45.840 --> 12:46.810
[Ji Feng]

13:03.120 --> 13:05.390
Feng is only fierce in words.

13:06.550 --> 13:07.880
Kaixin is considered to

13:08.480 --> 13:10.210
be controlled by him this time.

13:16.950 --> 13:18.440
I'm so mad!

13:18.870 --> 13:19.360
I...

13:20.670 --> 13:21.410
I'm angry.

13:22.510 --> 13:24.290
He actually bossed me around!

13:24.440 --> 13:25.700
Who does he think he is?

13:26.960 --> 13:27.890
Don't go too far.

13:28.150 --> 13:29.150
Me, going too far?

13:30.630 --> 13:32.270
When guests check into the hotel,

13:32.270 --> 13:35.600
the HSKP Department definitely
needs me to arrange things.

13:35.630 --> 13:36.360
But he

13:36.360 --> 13:37.340
didn't even ask,

13:37.440 --> 13:39.770
and directly named Xu Miyu to take charge.

13:40.240 --> 13:41.740
Does he treat me,
the Director of the HSKP Department,

13:41.740 --> 13:42.270
he...

13:43.000 --> 13:43.910
as a vase?

13:45.150 --> 13:46.150
You're not a vase,

13:46.870 --> 13:48.120
but a wine bottle.

13:50.610 --> 13:51.320
You...

13:51.840 --> 13:54.010
Brother, say a few words for me.

13:55.670 --> 13:58.880
Xu Miyu is the forewoman
of the executive floor.

13:59.150 --> 14:00.750
VIPs staying on the executive floor

14:00.750 --> 14:02.510
are naturally handled by Xu Miyu.

14:02.510 --> 14:03.940
What are you so upset about?

14:03.940 --> 14:04.610
Me?

14:04.630 --> 14:06.430
Of course I'm upset!

14:07.000 --> 14:08.530
Who doesn't know that woman

14:08.600 --> 14:10.000
is Mr. Ji's favorite?

14:10.440 --> 14:12.230
She gets all the spotlight?

14:12.390 --> 14:13.390
It's gone too far.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.270
The spotlight

14:15.380 --> 14:17.380
depends on how you let her take it.

14:18.270 --> 14:19.670
If you want her to shine,

14:20.560 --> 14:22.320
you let her shine the right way.

14:23.270 --> 14:24.470
If you want her

14:25.030 --> 14:26.510
to stumble,

14:27.330 --> 14:29.000
that's also an option.

14:29.620 --> 14:30.910
Right, Mr. Wei?

14:32.870 --> 14:34.030
What do you mean?

14:39.170 --> 14:40.910
Between Xu Miyu and Ji Feng,

14:40.910 --> 14:42.510
isn't there still you?

14:43.430 --> 14:46.230
You can just make some arrangements
in the middle,

14:47.930 --> 14:49.330
and set a trap for Xu Miyu.

14:50.010 --> 14:51.960
Will Ji Feng deal with it or not?

14:52.520 --> 14:53.390
If he doesn't handle it,

14:53.390 --> 14:54.510
he loses public support.

14:54.510 --> 14:55.530
If he does handle it,

14:55.530 --> 14:56.870
he's already short-staffed—

14:56.870 --> 14:58.060
he loses another person either way.

14:58.060 --> 14:59.030
Brilliant.

15:00.480 --> 15:02.210
You two are the brilliant ones.

15:05.930 --> 15:06.510
Come on.

15:06.840 --> 15:07.670
Stop drinking.

15:07.670 --> 15:08.780
A toast to you two.

15:08.960 --> 15:09.620
Bottoms up!

15:09.720 --> 15:10.870
Drink less.

15:13.200 --> 15:14.150
Think it over carefully.

15:14.150 --> 15:15.510
Do some real work.

15:17.270 --> 15:18.200
Kaixin.

15:23.990 --> 15:24.930
Ms. Xu,

15:25.510 --> 15:27.790
the executive floor
has been quite peaceful lately.

15:27.790 --> 15:28.600
How is it?

15:28.600 --> 15:30.400
Are you getting used to the work?

15:31.080 --> 15:32.320
I'm trying to adapt.

15:32.320 --> 15:33.030
Director,

15:33.360 --> 15:34.440
I'll keep working hard.

15:34.440 --> 15:35.150
Good.

15:35.190 --> 15:36.250
Very good.

15:37.390 --> 15:38.390
Right now,

15:38.390 --> 15:40.850
I have a good opportunity
for you to perform.

15:41.600 --> 15:42.460
It's like this.

15:42.790 --> 15:43.870
Next, our hotel

15:43.950 --> 15:45.790
will be hosting an important VIP client.

15:45.790 --> 15:46.550
Mr. Ji

15:46.550 --> 15:48.440
assigned this task to our HSKP Department.

15:48.440 --> 15:50.670
Now I give it to you.

15:51.520 --> 15:52.460
You should know

15:52.910 --> 15:55.440
this is a rare opportunity
to prove yourself.

15:55.670 --> 15:56.720
In our HSKP Department,

15:56.720 --> 15:59.600
many forewomen
want to show their faces.

16:00.080 --> 16:01.200
I have faith in you.

16:05.320 --> 16:06.080
This

16:06.130 --> 16:07.660
is the customer's profile.

16:08.080 --> 16:10.000
You must study it carefully
when you get back.

16:10.000 --> 16:11.080
Prepare well,

16:11.240 --> 16:13.370
and strive to make new contributions.

16:16.070 --> 16:17.200
Okay, Director.

16:18.240 --> 16:20.350
[Customer Information of Purong Hotel]

16:21.510 --> 16:22.310
What's wrong?

16:22.790 --> 16:25.440
You look like you're not very willing.

16:26.390 --> 16:27.290
No.

16:27.670 --> 16:29.080
Thank you for your favor, Director.

16:29.080 --> 16:30.030
Our executive floor

16:30.030 --> 16:31.910
will definitely provide
good reception service.

16:31.910 --> 16:32.430
Good.

16:33.150 --> 16:33.850
Ms. Xu,

16:34.370 --> 16:36.480
I have high hopes for you.

16:36.510 --> 16:38.820
Please make sure I won't

16:39.140 --> 16:40.320
lose face in front of Mr. Ji.

16:40.320 --> 16:41.030
Okay.

16:41.320 --> 16:42.250
I will do my best.

16:43.220 --> 16:43.910
Come on.

16:43.910 --> 16:45.080
Go back and prepare well.

16:45.080 --> 16:46.080
I'll be going now.

16:56.900 --> 16:59.270
[Purong Hotel]

16:58.600 --> 16:59.150
Mr. Qian,

16:59.440 --> 17:00.670
here are the client profiles
you asked me to print.

17:00.670 --> 17:01.460
Please take a look.

17:01.460 --> 17:05.740
[Director's Office]

17:01.910 --> 17:02.870
Keep them with you for now.

17:02.870 --> 17:04.680
But the notice says
this client is coming tomorrow.

17:04.680 --> 17:06.210
How should we arrange this?

17:07.720 --> 17:08.160
Well,

17:08.849 --> 17:10.579
ask everyone in the group chat.

17:11.030 --> 17:13.450
Give these materials to
whoever is willing to go.

17:13.450 --> 17:14.170
Okay.

17:18.990 --> 17:21.270
Notice: Colleagues, please check that

17:21.270 --> 17:22.680
the client's information is in the email.

17:22.680 --> 17:24.310
Please actively participate

17:24.310 --> 17:25.750
in the preparations for
hosting Libo Group's

17:25.750 --> 17:27.000
APAC CBO,

17:27.000 --> 17:28.569
Marcos Yang.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.510
Thank you for your cooperation—

17:30.510 --> 17:31.840
from sales department.

17:38.830 --> 17:39.550
What I sent you

17:39.550 --> 17:40.920
is the renewal contract drafted by Purong.

17:40.920 --> 17:42.580
Check it for any issues first.

17:44.720 --> 17:46.320
I'll talk to Mr. Wei.

17:46.610 --> 17:48.470
I'll let you know when I have news.

17:50.980 --> 17:51.620
Honey,

17:52.590 --> 17:54.510
don't be in a hurry to sign the contract.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.310
What's wrong?

18:03.720 --> 18:06.820
Purong Hotel is in a total mess right now.

18:07.120 --> 18:08.320
Don't get involved.

18:08.790 --> 18:10.440
Changing ownership
is next year's business.

18:10.440 --> 18:11.200
Besides,

18:11.200 --> 18:12.600
Mr. Wei is not an outsider.

18:12.600 --> 18:14.400
Let's just sign this year's contract.

18:14.400 --> 18:15.830
That's not how it works.

18:16.290 --> 18:18.830
Whether Wei Siyuan's position
is secure or not,

18:18.830 --> 18:20.070
it's hard to say.

18:20.620 --> 18:22.080
Anyway, just listen to me.

18:22.350 --> 18:24.350
Sign it a couple of days later, okay?

18:25.110 --> 18:26.070
Okay?

18:26.070 --> 18:27.000
Okay.

18:27.000 --> 18:28.460
I'll listen to you, honey.

18:31.310 --> 18:31.910
What is it?

18:31.980 --> 18:33.480
I have something good to show you.

18:33.480 --> 18:34.410
What good thing?

18:36.420 --> 18:37.540
[Yueting Real Estate:
Build A Home With Ingenuity]

18:38.750 --> 18:41.070
Where we live now
is convenient and affordable.

18:41.070 --> 18:42.270
Isn't it good enough?

18:42.850 --> 18:44.480
Look closely,

18:44.880 --> 18:46.680
this is a school district house.

18:47.310 --> 18:48.920
The Experimental Primary School,

18:48.920 --> 18:50.310
the Normal University
Affiliated Primary School,

18:50.310 --> 18:52.830
and several private primary schools
are all nearby.

18:52.830 --> 18:55.260
I just passed by
when I met a client today,

18:55.350 --> 18:57.180
and saw many people rushing to buy it.

18:57.180 --> 18:58.370
Look at this floor plan.

18:58.370 --> 18:59.900
[The highlight of the household]

18:58.750 --> 19:00.790
Every room faces south.

19:01.160 --> 19:02.590
Where else can you
find a floor plan like this?

19:02.590 --> 19:03.790
After the child is born,

19:03.790 --> 19:06.410
whether a nanny or our mom comes to help,

19:06.550 --> 19:08.240
don't they need a nice place to stay?

19:08.240 --> 19:09.640
Right, that makes sense.

19:09.640 --> 19:12.000
But the problem
is the child hasn't been born yet.

19:12.000 --> 19:13.590
It's too early for school.

19:14.790 --> 19:16.270
Now to go to primary school,

19:16.270 --> 19:18.870
you need 5 years of school district house
qualification in advance.

19:18.870 --> 19:20.310
You still think it's too early?

19:20.310 --> 19:21.620
You silly dad.

19:21.750 --> 19:23.500
Let's wait until I'm done with
this busy period.

19:23.500 --> 19:24.260
No.

19:24.560 --> 19:26.400
We have to go house hunting this weekend.

19:26.400 --> 19:28.860
Otherwise, this floor plan
will be sold out.

19:28.890 --> 19:29.870
Honey,

19:30.160 --> 19:32.310
I've been really busy at work lately.

19:35.550 --> 19:38.280
Which is more important,
the baby or the company?

19:39.750 --> 19:41.270
Which is more important,
the baby or the company?

19:41.270 --> 19:42.800
The baby is more important.

19:44.830 --> 19:47.030
Let's go take a look this weekend.

20:10.810 --> 20:12.890
[Health condition]
[Psychology health attention]

20:23.000 --> 20:23.720
Mr. Ji.

20:24.490 --> 20:26.200
How are you doing with the materials?

20:26.200 --> 20:27.110
Almost done.

20:27.110 --> 20:28.710
I'll review them twice more.

20:29.240 --> 20:30.550
Mr. Yang

20:30.550 --> 20:31.920
is Spanish-Chinese.

20:32.270 --> 20:34.720
He has a deep affection
for Chinese culture.

20:34.720 --> 20:36.550
He travels around the world all year round

20:36.550 --> 20:38.810
and has stayed in various luxury hotels.

20:39.110 --> 20:40.680
This time he comes to Shanghai

20:40.680 --> 20:42.340
and chooses our Purong Hotel.

20:42.460 --> 20:43.650
He has high expectations

20:43.650 --> 20:44.960
for this stay.

20:44.990 --> 20:46.950
Details are your strong suit.

20:46.970 --> 20:48.300
I'll leave this to you.

20:49.120 --> 20:50.280
I understand, Mr. Ji.

20:49.290 --> 20:55.720
[Receptionist]

20:50.300 --> 20:50.860
Okay.

20:54.790 --> 20:56.310
You're the only one here today?

20:56.310 --> 20:57.570
I'm on the night shift.

20:58.000 --> 20:58.680
Find someone

20:58.680 --> 21:00.740
to cover your shift and get some rest.

21:00.810 --> 21:02.170
I don't want you

21:02.310 --> 21:03.510
to look sleep-deprived tomorrow

21:03.510 --> 21:04.710
when receiving VIPs.

21:05.030 --> 21:05.670
Okay.

21:05.880 --> 21:06.350
Okay.

21:07.090 --> 21:08.500
[Receptionist]

21:13.230 --> 21:13.880
Mr. Ji,

21:14.310 --> 21:15.160
don't worry.

21:15.270 --> 21:17.480
Tomorrow, the executive floor
will definitely

21:17.480 --> 21:19.030
use our fullest enthusiasm,

21:19.030 --> 21:19.910
overcome all difficulties,

21:19.910 --> 21:21.710
and help you win this big client.

21:24.070 --> 21:24.790
Okay.

21:29.840 --> 21:35.730
[Purong Hotel]

21:34.480 --> 21:35.510
Hello, Mr. Ji.

21:35.510 --> 21:36.110
Hello.

21:47.340 --> 21:48.270
Morning, Mr. Ji.

21:53.110 --> 21:54.310
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

21:55.830 --> 21:57.760
I'm Lu Zhenzhen from the sales department.

21:57.760 --> 21:58.820
Do you remember me?

21:59.000 --> 22:02.130
My mother-in-law
just had her 60th birthday last month.

22:02.160 --> 22:02.760
Of course.

22:03.110 --> 22:04.510
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

22:04.660 --> 22:06.350
I just transferred to
the sales department.

22:06.350 --> 22:08.050
Please take care of me, Mr. Ji.

22:10.070 --> 22:11.110
Hello, Ms. Xu.

22:14.720 --> 22:15.410
Mr. Ji,

22:15.440 --> 22:16.310
I won't let

22:16.310 --> 22:18.910
any personal feelings interfere with
my work.

22:26.310 --> 22:27.160
Oh my god.

22:27.310 --> 22:29.350
The wife and the mistress
are in the same frame.

22:29.350 --> 22:30.680
Are they going to fight?

22:49.370 --> 22:50.290
Marcos,

22:51.630 --> 22:53.290
I'm great to see you in Shanghai.

22:53.290 --> 22:54.220
Long time no see.

22:55.260 --> 22:56.460
Hello, I am Zhen,

22:56.480 --> 22:59.480
the sales representative
from Purong Hotel.

22:59.510 --> 23:01.030
After the long journey,

23:01.050 --> 23:05.440
would you prefer to take a rest
or grab something to eat first?

23:05.470 --> 23:06.670
I'll rest first.

23:09.260 --> 23:11.020
Welcome, Mr. Marcos.

23:11.040 --> 23:12.310
I'll take you to your room.

23:12.310 --> 23:13.310
This way, please.

23:13.550 --> 23:14.220
Thank you.

23:26.570 --> 23:28.170
Welcome.

23:28.650 --> 23:31.020
Good morning, Mr. Yang.

23:31.310 --> 23:34.830
I'm the director of the rooms.

23:35.240 --> 23:38.280
My name is Feng Kaixin.

23:40.070 --> 23:41.030
Hello, Mr. Feng.

23:41.940 --> 23:43.440
Mr. Yang, your Chinese is so good.

23:43.440 --> 23:44.130
Great.

23:45.110 --> 23:46.510
Mr. Yang, please come in.

23:57.710 --> 23:58.470
Excuse me.

24:08.790 --> 24:09.350
Marcos,

24:10.270 --> 24:11.640
after such a long flight,

24:11.640 --> 24:12.510
you must be hungry.

24:12.510 --> 24:14.840
You can go to the restaurant
for some food.

24:15.720 --> 24:17.310
No need to be so complicated.

24:17.310 --> 24:18.770
I'll just grab a bite here.

24:19.720 --> 24:22.040
There are ready-made sandwiches
in the Executive Lounge.

24:22.040 --> 24:23.190
Cold food is bad for the stomach.

24:23.190 --> 24:24.550
Marcos has a weak stomach.

24:24.550 --> 24:26.750
The Executive Lounge can make hot food.

24:27.270 --> 24:28.070
How long will it take?

24:28.070 --> 24:28.720
Anytime.

24:28.720 --> 24:30.450
Serve the dishes immediately.

24:54.690 --> 24:55.530
Master Yue,

24:55.880 --> 24:56.750
did anyone else give you

24:56.750 --> 24:58.000
the guest's dietary restrictions?

24:58.000 --> 24:58.640
No.

25:25.160 --> 25:26.090
Okay, thank you.

25:28.110 --> 25:28.960
Your business banquet

25:28.960 --> 25:31.890
is actually very suitable
to be held at Purong Hotel.

25:32.720 --> 25:35.880
I think your hotel
is indeed quite tasteful.

25:36.160 --> 25:37.790
It's just that the other company
has already

25:37.790 --> 25:39.310
booked a restaurant in advance.

25:39.310 --> 25:41.160
It's okay. There will be
other opportunities in the future.

25:41.160 --> 25:41.790
It's a pity.

25:41.790 --> 25:43.920
There will be opportunities anytime.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.350
Ms. Xu.

25:47.240 --> 25:48.750
This salad is a bit too much.

25:48.750 --> 25:50.280
I'll portion it out for you.

25:50.550 --> 25:51.150
Thank you.

25:58.350 --> 25:59.070
Thank you.

25:59.480 --> 26:01.160
Swap out the egg and mayonnaise,

26:01.160 --> 26:02.720
and replace them with
Japanese roasted sesame dressing

26:02.720 --> 26:03.610
and chicken breast.

26:03.610 --> 26:04.590
Halve the portion.

26:04.590 --> 26:05.160
Make it fast.

26:05.160 --> 26:05.790
Okay.

26:09.790 --> 26:10.400
Thank you.

26:19.830 --> 26:21.590
I don't mean to look down on you.

26:21.960 --> 26:24.140
At this level, you're still managing to

26:24.140 --> 26:26.600
get by as a forewoman
on the executive floor?

26:34.030 --> 26:35.160
We'd hate to disturb you.

26:35.160 --> 26:36.090
Have a good rest.

26:53.440 --> 26:54.160
Ms. Xu,

26:54.590 --> 26:55.650
your explanation?

26:55.790 --> 26:56.790
I am sorry, Mr. Ji.

26:57.270 --> 26:59.800
The person you should
apologize to is Marcos.

27:02.070 --> 27:03.350
But on my documents...

27:03.370 --> 27:04.550
Ms. Xu,

27:05.000 --> 27:07.550
I told you again and again yesterday

27:07.550 --> 27:08.920
and emphasized

27:08.920 --> 27:10.550
the importance of this task.

27:10.550 --> 27:12.350
How could you still make
such an amateur mistake?

27:12.350 --> 27:14.610
I handed such an important client to you.

27:14.630 --> 27:16.480
It is clearly written in the documents

27:16.480 --> 27:18.310
that Marcos is allergic to pollen

27:18.310 --> 27:19.750
and eggs.

27:19.750 --> 27:21.920
You didn't even look at
such important information.

27:21.920 --> 27:23.830
Do you have any sense of
responsibility for your work?

27:23.830 --> 27:25.140
You brought shame to our executive floor,

27:25.140 --> 27:25.750
no,

27:25.780 --> 27:28.220
the entire HSKP Department.

27:28.350 --> 27:30.310
Mr. Feng, the documents
you gave me clearly...

27:30.310 --> 27:31.630
You're still explaining, huh?

27:31.630 --> 27:32.290
Look at you,

27:32.490 --> 27:33.720
still trying to pass the buck to me.

27:33.720 --> 27:34.850
If it weren't for me

27:34.870 --> 27:37.180
and Mr. Ji taking charge
on the spot today,

27:37.180 --> 27:40.380
who knows how much loss the hotel
would have suffered?

27:40.410 --> 27:41.760
Look at your working attitude

27:41.760 --> 27:42.520
and level.

27:42.550 --> 27:45.680
Do you still deserve to be
an executive floor forewoman?

27:46.190 --> 27:47.080
Ms. Xu,

27:47.560 --> 27:48.780
can you handle it well?

27:48.780 --> 27:49.430
I can.

27:49.970 --> 27:51.570
I'll trust you one more time.

27:55.720 --> 27:56.940
Just let it go?

28:04.070 --> 28:04.790
Ms. Xu,

28:04.790 --> 28:06.670
Mr. Ji wants to see you in his office.

28:06.670 --> 28:07.530
I was just heading there.

28:07.280 --> 28:08.990
[Receptionist]

28:11.480 --> 28:11.940
Come in.

28:13.530 --> 28:14.340
Mr. Ji,

28:15.680 --> 28:17.510
I've read this document over ten times,

28:17.510 --> 28:18.640
and I've memorized it.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.720
It really doesn't mention

28:19.720 --> 28:21.310
Marcos' food allergies.

28:24.910 --> 28:25.670
Here.

28:29.580 --> 28:31.380
[Allergies: allergic to pollen and eggs.]

28:34.590 --> 28:35.660
[Professional Background]

28:35.110 --> 28:35.720
Wait,

28:36.070 --> 28:37.660
this is not my file.

28:37.790 --> 28:38.510
I highlighted my copy of the materials

28:38.510 --> 28:40.310
with a marker.

28:44.690 --> 28:48.010
[Health status] [Mental health concerns]

28:48.830 --> 28:49.480
Look.

28:50.030 --> 28:51.480
Fortunately, I have a photo.

28:51.480 --> 28:53.220
It was marked with a highlighter.

28:52.620 --> 28:53.740
[Health status]

28:54.680 --> 28:55.400
Not bad.

28:55.510 --> 28:56.710
You reacted quickly.

28:58.110 --> 29:00.070
I know this was not your fault.

29:00.640 --> 29:01.570
I called you here

29:01.750 --> 29:03.110
to give you a new one.

29:03.310 --> 29:04.780
Then just now...

29:05.030 --> 29:06.410
You were eager to prove yourself,

29:06.410 --> 29:08.410
and I wanted to see what you could do.

29:08.550 --> 29:09.470
Mr. Ji.

29:09.510 --> 29:09.980
All right.

29:09.980 --> 29:11.640
That's the end of this matter.

29:12.240 --> 29:14.830
It's safer if you use my version.

29:15.830 --> 29:17.030
For all future reception work,

29:17.030 --> 29:18.490
you report directly to me.

29:18.550 --> 29:19.320
Understood?

29:21.350 --> 29:22.160
Understood.

29:23.350 --> 29:24.350
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

29:46.260 --> 29:47.540
Mr. Marcos,

29:47.590 --> 29:48.960
I know that Libo Group

29:48.960 --> 29:51.540
is known globally for its long-termism.

29:51.750 --> 29:54.350
The acquisition of Taisheng Metropolis
seven years ago

29:54.350 --> 29:56.240
is unsurpassed among

29:56.240 --> 29:58.100
global construction companies.

29:58.160 --> 30:00.370
Has your hotel cooperated with Libo?

30:00.550 --> 30:01.190
Of course.

30:01.340 --> 30:03.160
Our hotel hosted the annual meeting

30:03.160 --> 30:03.960
of Libo Group's

30:03.960 --> 30:06.640
branch in Shanghai, China last year.

30:06.640 --> 30:08.790
We are also negotiating

30:08.790 --> 30:10.750
with Libo Group's partner,
Shenjiang Industry,

30:10.750 --> 30:12.010
on some projects.

30:12.400 --> 30:13.180
Sorry,

30:14.830 --> 30:15.480
I'm late.

30:15.590 --> 30:17.050
Sorry to keep you waiting.

30:17.750 --> 30:18.360
How is it?

30:19.240 --> 30:20.570
Are you used to the food?

30:20.620 --> 30:21.750
This meat is not bad.

30:21.960 --> 30:23.140
It's especially tender
when I bite into it.

30:23.140 --> 30:24.070
I really like it.

30:25.820 --> 30:27.980
This is our hotel's signature dish.

30:28.540 --> 30:31.270
The veal shank is very delicious.

30:31.480 --> 30:34.030
It was carefully prepared for you

30:34.030 --> 30:35.630
by a chef in our kitchen who specializes

30:35.630 --> 30:36.930
in Mediterranean cuisine.

30:36.930 --> 30:37.890
So thoughtful.

30:40.350 --> 30:41.280
Braised prawns.

30:42.260 --> 30:42.980
Try it.

30:49.640 --> 30:51.110
The flavor is quite rich.

30:52.880 --> 30:54.000
How was it made?

30:54.480 --> 30:55.780
It

30:57.170 --> 30:58.100
is made by our...

30:58.760 --> 31:00.040
This cuisine

31:00.070 --> 31:01.670
mainly depends on the sauce.

31:01.960 --> 31:03.640
In most places, the sauce

31:03.640 --> 31:06.380
is made by mixing store-bought ketchup.

31:06.410 --> 31:08.480
But in our kitchen, the sauce is made

31:08.480 --> 31:10.310
by simmering wild mushroom broth together

31:10.310 --> 31:12.590
with fresh tomatoes,

31:12.590 --> 31:14.730
so it has a very seasonal flavor.

31:14.750 --> 31:17.600
So did you arrange

31:18.910 --> 31:20.340
these dishes?

31:20.390 --> 31:23.550
I learned that you prefer Chinese cuisine,

31:23.770 --> 31:25.960
and you also like
various kinds of seafood.

31:25.960 --> 31:27.350
So for tonight's menu,

31:27.350 --> 31:30.400
most of it is Chinese-style seafood.

31:34.670 --> 31:35.500
Thank you.

31:35.800 --> 31:36.990
I'm glad you like it.

31:37.550 --> 31:38.380
I love it.

31:39.410 --> 31:40.410
And thank you too.

31:40.570 --> 31:42.030
You are all like my family.

31:42.240 --> 31:44.160
You know me very well.

31:44.550 --> 31:45.350
Right, Kenny?

31:46.110 --> 31:46.790
Of course.

31:47.430 --> 31:49.190
The service staff you trained

31:49.210 --> 31:51.350
have never disappointed me.

31:51.640 --> 31:53.240
You're flattering us.

31:53.260 --> 31:53.830
Don't be.

31:53.830 --> 31:54.550
Come.

31:54.650 --> 31:55.590
Cheers.

31:55.620 --> 31:57.550
It's really great.

31:58.050 --> 31:59.250
As long as you like it.

32:10.940 --> 32:14.410
[Receipt]

32:14.410 --> 32:16.030
[Shang PIN JIN HUO JI LU BIAO]

32:18.470 --> 32:19.070
Who is it?

32:19.680 --> 32:20.200
Xue Rui!

32:20.990 --> 32:21.530
Xue...

32:21.970 --> 32:22.830
Mr. Xue?

32:22.210 --> 32:24.120
[Shang PIN JIN HUO JI LU BIAO] [Receipt]

32:22.960 --> 32:24.070
Wait a moment!

32:27.910 --> 32:28.400
Coming.

32:29.070 --> 32:29.640
Coming.

32:32.090 --> 32:32.860
Mr. Chen.

32:32.960 --> 32:34.110
Why is your door locked?

32:34.110 --> 32:34.960
What are you hiding?

32:34.960 --> 32:36.750
Mr. Xue, why are you here?

32:36.990 --> 32:38.610
It's a bit chaotic.

32:38.800 --> 32:39.670
It will

32:39.830 --> 32:41.120
ruin

32:41.480 --> 32:42.240
your suit.

32:42.240 --> 32:44.240
Are you treating me like a stranger?

32:44.830 --> 32:45.960
It's a work uniform.

32:46.300 --> 32:47.160
Did you forget?

32:47.200 --> 32:48.800
We used to come here
at the end of every month

32:48.800 --> 32:50.520
to settle accounts.

32:50.920 --> 32:51.510
Right.

32:51.870 --> 32:55.000
You were in charge of
the purchasing accounts back then.

32:57.030 --> 32:58.160
This place is great.

32:58.590 --> 32:59.970
This is the granary of Purong Hotel.

32:59.970 --> 33:01.160
It is a treasured place.

33:01.160 --> 33:02.760
I want to live here every day.

33:03.590 --> 33:04.450
How is it going?

33:04.720 --> 33:05.450
Are you busy?

33:05.660 --> 33:06.640
Business is okay.

33:06.640 --> 33:07.790
We have a few tables for lunch.

33:07.790 --> 33:08.380
But,

33:08.480 --> 33:10.010
they are all regular customers.

33:10.010 --> 33:10.910
No new ones.

33:12.790 --> 33:15.120
How much revenue do you make during lunch?

33:21.590 --> 33:22.160
Brother Chen,

33:22.160 --> 33:24.550
can you let me see your purchase orders?

33:25.720 --> 33:27.160
I'm afraid not.

33:27.780 --> 33:28.910
Chef Jia is not here.

33:29.310 --> 33:30.350
I can't make the call.

33:30.350 --> 33:31.400
Come on.

33:31.720 --> 33:34.070
You are the manager
of the purchasing department.

33:34.070 --> 33:35.510
You can't even make this call?

33:35.510 --> 33:37.070
What purchasing department manager?

33:37.070 --> 33:38.880
I'm just a grocery shopper.

33:41.940 --> 33:42.400
Okay.

33:42.400 --> 33:43.500
I won't make things difficult for you.

33:43.500 --> 33:44.240
Look,

33:44.400 --> 33:45.590
when Chef Jia comes back,

33:45.590 --> 33:47.880
ask him to prepare the purchase order

33:47.880 --> 33:49.280
and hand it in to me today.

33:49.650 --> 33:50.070
No.

33:50.090 --> 33:51.020
This won't do.

33:52.310 --> 33:52.880
Brother,

33:53.450 --> 33:54.830
let me be honest with you.

33:54.830 --> 33:56.340
The new boss

33:56.640 --> 33:59.750
has been looking at
the Chinese restaurant's bills lately.

33:59.750 --> 34:01.280
They are really rushing me.

34:01.490 --> 34:02.620
Do me a favor.

34:02.640 --> 34:03.500
After Chef Jia comes back,

34:03.500 --> 34:05.560
have him prepare it and hand it over to me

34:05.560 --> 34:06.760
so I can report back

34:08.080 --> 34:08.969
and get through this.

34:08.969 --> 34:09.739
I see.

34:11.630 --> 34:12.150
All right.

34:12.150 --> 34:13.480
I will definitely tell him.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.630
Okay, thanks.

34:14.630 --> 34:15.230
I'll let you get back to work.

34:15.230 --> 34:16.030
It's nothing.

34:16.030 --> 34:16.949
The cup.

34:17.190 --> 34:17.790
Thank you.

34:18.110 --> 34:19.040
Okay, take care.

34:19.250 --> 34:19.810
Bye.

34:19.840 --> 34:20.590
Bye.

34:43.040 --> 34:43.780
How did it go?

34:45.699 --> 34:46.630
I'm already this old,

34:46.630 --> 34:47.710
and I still have to
play spy games with you.

34:47.710 --> 34:49.510
Good thing I have strong nerves.

34:50.900 --> 34:52.900
I said everything you told me to say.

34:53.070 --> 34:54.199
But your goal

34:54.400 --> 34:56.510
definitely isn't
just the purchase order, right?

34:56.510 --> 34:57.710
You know me best, Rui.

34:59.200 --> 35:01.600
Are you still not going to
tell me your plan?

35:07.070 --> 35:07.480
Here.

35:11.100 --> 35:14.570
[Personnel Registration
Form of Purong Hotel]

35:12.360 --> 35:13.280
Jia Shikun

35:13.740 --> 35:15.940
claims to be a disciple
of Huaiyang cuisine master Gu Shanghong.

35:14.600 --> 35:15.780
[Name: Jia Shikun]

35:16.440 --> 35:18.230
Relying on his signature dish—
salted pork rib soup with bamboo shoots—

35:18.230 --> 35:20.000
said to be a top specialty in Shanghai,

35:20.000 --> 35:20.800
he has been secretly taking advantage of

35:20.800 --> 35:23.730
the hotel for years,
and no one has dared to touch him.

35:24.320 --> 35:26.980
To solve the problem
of our Chinese restaurant,

35:27.070 --> 35:28.330
he must be eliminated.

35:29.670 --> 35:31.320
I know about Jia Shikun's problem.

35:31.320 --> 35:32.520
But if you touch him,

35:32.590 --> 35:34.230
the board won't agree.

35:34.480 --> 35:36.440
So I want him to leave by himself.

35:38.790 --> 35:41.050
How are you so sure
he'll leave on his own?

35:41.230 --> 35:43.070
He's hot-tempered

35:43.190 --> 35:44.480
and cares most about his reputation.

35:44.480 --> 35:46.960
Even Wei Siyuan
takes a detour when he sees him.

35:46.960 --> 35:48.510
A newly appointed manager,

35:48.760 --> 35:51.190
recklessly trying to use him as an example

35:51.190 --> 35:53.070
and making him hand over
the account books...

35:53.070 --> 35:55.150
Do you think he'll be furious

35:55.150 --> 35:57.150
and try to assert dominance over me?

35:57.920 --> 35:59.510
That's all your guess.

35:59.710 --> 36:01.980
I asked a headhunter I know.

36:02.320 --> 36:04.630
There are quite a few hotels
trying to recruit him this month,

36:04.630 --> 36:06.880
including Kuanli Hotel.

36:09.360 --> 36:11.920
I'm just giving him a little push.

36:17.870 --> 36:19.190
Be quick about it!

36:20.070 --> 36:20.670
Chef!

36:20.670 --> 36:21.870
You're finally here.

36:22.030 --> 36:24.160
I've been looking for you everywhere.

36:30.360 --> 36:31.290
You cut it so big?

36:31.320 --> 36:32.590
You want to choke someone?

36:32.590 --> 36:33.150
Recut it!

36:36.590 --> 36:37.590
What is it? Speak.

36:37.640 --> 36:38.320
Speak.

36:39.190 --> 36:41.190
The higher-ups are investigating.

36:41.760 --> 36:42.690
The higher-ups?

36:42.880 --> 36:43.510
Yes.

36:46.630 --> 36:47.850
Is it the guy surnamed Ji?

36:47.850 --> 36:48.670
Yes.

36:50.960 --> 36:52.300
The new boss is taking office

36:52.300 --> 36:54.500
and throwing his weight around my turf?

36:55.400 --> 36:57.590
They're forcing us
to hand in the list today.

36:57.590 --> 36:59.510
Why don't we just fool them a bit

36:59.510 --> 37:00.240
and let it go?

37:00.920 --> 37:01.980
If you want to play,

37:02.110 --> 37:03.190
go play with him.

37:03.350 --> 37:04.340
I won't.

37:05.520 --> 37:06.920
Chef, don't be like this.

37:07.510 --> 37:08.840
Don't talk to me, I quit.

37:09.030 --> 37:09.480
Listen to me.

37:09.480 --> 37:11.550
You suppress this matter first.

37:11.550 --> 37:13.230
We will always have a way out later.

37:13.230 --> 37:14.020
Take what?

37:14.150 --> 37:14.840
What do we do?

37:14.840 --> 37:15.590
-What should I tell him?
-Calm down.

37:15.590 --> 37:16.070
I'll talk to him.

37:16.070 --> 37:16.630
I will tell him.

37:16.630 --> 37:17.440
Don't be in a rush to leave.

37:17.440 --> 37:17.960
Well..

37:17.960 --> 37:18.820
Right, just...

37:20.580 --> 37:21.780
Good for you.

37:22.070 --> 37:23.380
You did so much on your own,

37:23.380 --> 37:24.960
and didn't tell me anything.

37:24.960 --> 37:25.760
If I had told you,

37:25.760 --> 37:27.190
Rui, would you still have

37:27.190 --> 37:30.590
such excellent acting skills
in the purchasing department?

37:33.120 --> 37:36.480
Do you have a suitable chef?

37:38.250 --> 37:40.310
I have someone I'd like to try hiring.

37:48.110 --> 37:49.440
At Duan Aoxiang's banquet,

37:48.360 --> 37:50.820
[Personnel Registration
Form of Purong Hotel]

37:49.440 --> 37:50.640
I saw her creativity.

37:50.760 --> 37:51.750
She graduated
from Le Cordon Bleu in France.

37:50.840 --> 37:52.430
[Name: Li Qiaoqi]

37:51.780 --> 37:53.070
She has ideas and she's capable.

37:53.070 --> 37:56.530
And I heard she has a particularly
good relationship with you.

38:00.440 --> 38:01.070
Yes.

38:01.070 --> 38:02.320
I know her quite well.

38:02.550 --> 38:03.880
She's straightforward

38:03.920 --> 38:05.030
and a doer.

38:05.760 --> 38:07.070
She can definitely be trusted.

38:07.070 --> 38:08.380
Once Jia Shikun leaves,

38:08.380 --> 38:10.150
he will definitely
take his kitchen staff with him.

38:10.150 --> 38:11.710
As long as we give her more time

38:11.710 --> 38:12.550
and trust her,

38:12.710 --> 38:14.570
she can slowly build her own team.

38:14.710 --> 38:15.480
In that case,

38:15.480 --> 38:16.210
we...

38:17.000 --> 38:17.760
Come in.

38:18.920 --> 38:20.320
Mr. Ji, Director Lu is...

38:20.840 --> 38:21.240
Mr. Ji,

38:23.070 --> 38:24.350
at 6:30 tonight,

38:24.550 --> 38:26.030
Mr. Marcos' business banquet

38:26.030 --> 38:28.000
will be changed to
the small banquet hall in our hotel.

38:26.880 --> 38:28.350
[Banquet Hall Application]

38:28.000 --> 38:28.670
A total of five tables.

38:28.670 --> 38:29.530
Please sign it.

38:30.960 --> 38:31.440
Are you sure?

38:31.440 --> 38:32.000
I'm sure.

38:32.260 --> 38:33.630
It took me a whole day

38:33.630 --> 38:35.550
to finally convince Mr. Marcos

38:35.550 --> 38:37.150
to move the banquet to our hotel.

38:35.830 --> 38:37.200
[Banquet Hall Application]
[General Manager's Approval: Approved]

38:37.150 --> 38:38.960
There will be many big shots tonight.

38:38.960 --> 38:40.190
Top executives from
the construction, mining,

38:39.840 --> 38:40.740
[Banquet invitation request department:
Sales Department]
[General Manager: Ji Feng]

38:40.190 --> 38:42.590
and real estate industries will be here.

38:42.590 --> 38:43.760
This is a very rare

38:43.760 --> 38:44.920
promotional opportunity for us.

38:44.920 --> 38:46.760
You are in charge of this banquet.

38:46.760 --> 38:48.260
Report to me if anything comes up.

38:48.260 --> 38:48.900
Rui.

38:52.550 --> 38:54.360
Director Lu picked a great time to come.

38:54.360 --> 38:56.280
Jia Shikun might not have left today.

38:56.280 --> 38:58.300
With such a good chance to set me up,

38:58.320 --> 39:00.080
how many people do you think
are left in the kitchen?

39:00.080 --> 39:00.830
What should we do then?

39:00.830 --> 39:02.150
Should we ask HR?

39:02.190 --> 39:04.110
Didn't you say we should
let Li Qiaoqi have a try?

39:04.110 --> 39:05.150
Now is the chance.

39:05.150 --> 39:07.350
Let's see if she can seize
the opportunity.

39:07.350 --> 39:08.340
She can do it.

39:07.690 --> 39:10.740
[Dinner menu] [Cold dishes] [Hot dishes]
[Staple food][Soup]

39:13.290 --> 39:15.390
How long does it take
to cook a five-table dinner?

39:15.390 --> 39:16.790
It's not a matter of time.

39:17.190 --> 39:18.070
You saw it too.

39:18.070 --> 39:20.310
Chef Jia took more than
half of the kitchen staff away.

39:20.310 --> 39:21.240
I need manpower.

39:21.850 --> 39:22.760
How many do you need?

39:22.760 --> 39:23.780
I want three Sous Chefs,

39:23.780 --> 39:24.840
and a dessert chef.

39:25.460 --> 39:26.600
I can't give you three.

39:26.600 --> 39:27.610
I'll give you one first,

39:27.610 --> 39:30.760
and I'll transfer the rest
to you from other departments.

39:30.760 --> 39:31.280
Okay.

39:31.670 --> 39:33.220
Mr. Ji, Mr. Xue.

39:33.480 --> 39:34.060
What is it?

39:34.060 --> 39:36.550
I just went to see
Manager Chen from procurement

39:36.550 --> 39:38.550
to get him to sign the guests'
dietary restrictions list.

39:38.550 --> 39:41.030
I happened to see him
locking the door and leaving,

39:41.030 --> 39:42.340
so I came to ask what happened.
